res_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6966d41afbda50b068d29e15_check-square.svg" alt="" class="image-27"/></div><div class="text-block-54">Fast, free shipping</div></div><div class="pricing-features_item"><div class="pricing-features_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6966d41afbda50b068d29e15_check-square.svg" alt="" class="image-27"/></div><div class="text-block-54">All sizes XS-3XL available</div></div><div class="pricing-features_item"><div class="pricing-features_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6966d41afbda50b068d29e15_check-square.svg" alt="" class="image-27"/></div><div class="text-block-54">Keep everything from your box</div></div><div class="pricing-features_item"><div class="pricing-features_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6966d41afbda50b068d29e15_check-square.svg" alt="" class="image-27"/></div><div class="text-block-54">Preview and swap before shipping</div></div><div class="pricing-features_item"><div class="pricing-features_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6966d41afbda50b068d29e15_check-square.svg" alt="" class="image-27"/></div><div class="text-block-54">Skip, pause or cancel anytime</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="button_wrap"><a href="/get-started" class="button-generic w-button">Join Now</a><a href="/how-it-works" class="link-7">Learn More</a></div></div><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container hiw w-container"><div class="text-block-53">How ThreadBeast Works</div><div class="hiw_grid"><div class="hiw_item"><div class="hiw_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/69673511f0b4e2b7f0db84a0_hiw-icon-set-your-style.svg" alt="" class="image-28"/></div><div class="text-block-55">Set Your Style</div><p class="paragraph-3">Shopping takes forever. Tell us what you like once, and we do the hard work for you.</p></div><div class="hiw_item"><div class="hiw_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/69673511f0b4e2b7f0db84a1_hiw-icon-review-your-drop.svg" alt="" class="image-28"/></div><div class="text-block-55">Review Your Drop</div><p class="paragraph-3">Your stylist picks, you approve. Don&#x27;t love something? Swap it out before it ships.</p></div><div class="hiw_item"><div class="hiw_icon-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/69673511f0b4e2b7f0db849f_hiw-icon-refresh-your-rotation.svg" alt="" class="image-28"/></div><div class="text-block-55">Refresh Your Rotation</div><p class="paragraph-3">Stop wearing the same three shirts. We keep your look fresh so you always stand out.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="section explore-collection"><div class="section_header-3"><div class="label-wrapper-6"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6967368b76ddf52952a3fb8c_left.svg" alt="" class="label-svg-2"/><div class="label-light">the clothes</div><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/6967368b76ddf52952a3fb8b_right.svg" alt="" class="label-svg-2"/></div><div class="section-small-header-light">Explore the Collection</div><div class="section-parapgraph-light">How will you fill your first box?</div></div><div class="promo_scroll_track"><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c493eb" href="/subcategories/jackets" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4b_home-collection-jackets-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4b_home-collection-jackets.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4b_home-collection-jackets.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">jackets</div></div></div></a><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c493f4" href="/subcategories/flannels" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f47_home-collection-flannels-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f47_home-collection-flannels.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f47_home-collection-flannels.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">flannels</div></div></div></a><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c493fd" href="/subcategories/vests" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f43_home-collection-vests-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f43_home-collection-vests.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f43_home-collection-vests.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">vests</div></div></div></a><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c49406" href="/subcategories/hoodies" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f57_home-collection-hoodies-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f57_home-collection-hoodies.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f57_home-collection-hoodies.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">hoodies</div></div></div></a><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c4940f" href="/subcategories/pants" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4f_home-collection-pants-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4f_home-collection-pants.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f4f_home-collection-pants.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">Pants</div></div></div></a><a data-w-id="0a7d2563-6c6e-a743-2221-dc3d71c49418" href="/subcategories/jeans" class="promo_card_v2 w-inline-block"><div class="promo_image_wrapper"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f53_home-collection-jeans-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f53_home-collection-jeans.jpg 768w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696736c5719fa254545a8f53_home-collection-jeans.jpg" loading="lazy" class="promo_bg_image_v2"/></div><div class="promo_content"><div class="promo_button_v2"><div class="text-block-62">Jeans</div></div></div></a></div></section><section class="section email-capture bg-neutral-200"><div class="container email-capture"><div><img sizes="(max-width: 757px) 100vw, 757px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696737ef569649991c8bbace_hanger-icon-lightning-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696737ef569649991c8bbace_hanger-icon-lightning.png 757w" alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/696737ef569649991c8bbace_hanger-icon-lightning.png" loading="lazy" class="image-23"/></div><div class="div-block-37"><div class="text-block-48"><strong class="bold-text-4">GET QUICK STYLE TIP EMAILS</strong></div><div class="text-block-49">Layering. Silhouettes. Making basics look expensive. 30 seconds, you&#x27;re out.</div></div><div class="form-block-5 w-form"><form id="email-form" name="email-form" data-name="Email Form" method="post" data-klaviyo-list-id="XXkHYK" class="klaviyo-form" data-wf-page-id="67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcab26" data-wf-element-id="1211018c-a8c5-1a5e-7805-6240a9897a65"><input class="text-field w-input" maxlength="256" name="email" data-name="email" placeholder="Your email*" type="email" id="email" required=""/><input type="submit" data-wait="Please wait..." class="submit-button w-button" value="Submit"/><div class="w-embed w-script"><script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
  const form = document.getElementById('email-form');
  if (!form) return;

  form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    // 1. Prevent Webflow from taking over
    e.preventDefault();
    e.stopImmediatePropagation();

    const emailValue = form.querySelector('input[name="email"]').value;
    const listId = "XXkHYK"; 
    const companyId = "RKi7T2";

    // 2. Build the body as URL-encoded data (Standard for AJAX endpoint)
    const formData = new URLSearchParams();
    formData.append('g', listId);
    formData.append('email', emailValue);
    formData.append('$fields', '$source');
    formData.append('$source', 'Webflow Form');

    // 3. Fire the request
    fetch(`https://manage.kmail-lists.com/ajax/subscriptions/subscribe?a=${companyId}`, {
      method: 'POST',
      body: formData,
      headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'
      }
    })
    .then(res => {
      // 4. On success, show the Webflow success message
      form.style.display = 'none';
      const wrapper = form.closest('.w-form');
      if (wrapper) {
        wrapper.querySelector('.w-form-done').style.display = 'block';
      }
    })
    .catch(err => {
      console.error('Klaviyo Error:', err);
      const wrapper = form.closest('.w-form');
      if (wrapper) {
        wrapper.querySelector('.w-form-fail').style.display = 'block';
      }
    });
  });
});
</script></div></form><div class="w-form-done"><div>Thank you! Your submission has been received!</div></div><div class="w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div></div></section></main><footer aria-label="tiktok" class="footer-section"><div class="container grid"><div id="w-node-_73c87ccf-69c8-d53d-9241-241543a429d2-654d2164" class="column"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="footer-brand w-nav-brand w--current"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67cfffc29d79bb37e5bcaae3/67dc7eaff0365b1919707637_Layer_1%20(3).svg" loading="lazy" alt="ThreadBeast Logo" class="footer-logo"/></a></div><div id="w-node-_39f7ee8f-4ee5-686e-ad84-809bfec12dc5-654d2164" class="column"><h3 class="footer-heading heading-style-h6">threadbeast</h3><div class="footer-link-wrapper"><a href="/community" class="footer-link">community</a><a href="/how-it-works" class="footer-link">how it works</a><a href="#" class="footer-link display-none">our mission</a><a href="/reviews" class="footer-link">reviews</a><a href="https://help.threadbeast.com/en/" target="_blank" class="footer-link">help</a><a href="/faq" class="footer-link">faq</a></div></div><div id="w-node-a5e4f806-ebe7-5af0-0fab-1fe4fe1a7c0b-654d2164" class="column"><h4 class="footer-heading heading-style-h6">styles</h4><div class="footer-link-wrapper"><a href="/styles/streetwear" class="footer-link">streetwear</a><a href="/styles/contemporary" class="footer-link">contemporary</a><a href="/styles/heritage" class="footer-link">heritage</a></div></div><div id="w-node-_41dc03bc-97f8-065c-ce1a-db77bb33ada0-654d2164" class="column"><h5 class="footer-heading heading-style-h6">SOCIAL</h5><div class="footer-link-wrapper"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/threadbeast/?hl=en" target="_blank" class="footer-link">INSTAGRAM</a><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@threadbeast" target="_blank" class="footer-link">TikTok</a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@threadbeast" target="_blank" class="footer-link">